* 0.2 *

* Added support for 'icarus' AntMiner devices

* 0.3 *

* Auto kernel detach in place... working much better on some Linux devices with certain libusb builds.

* 0.4 *

* Stratum connection pooling with priority and weight
* BitFury support (Nanofury and Blue/RedFury)
* Started development on CGMiner API
* Various stability and performance fixes
* More accurate timeouts and identity failure